Penetration Testing Linux Distributions
• Kali Linux: You can download Kali Linux from
https://www.kali.org. Offensive Security released a
free open source book and course about how to
install, customize, and use Kali Linux. The book and
the course can be accessed at https://kali.training.

• Parrot Security OS: You can download Parrot from
https://www.parrotsec.org and access the
documentation at https://docs.parrotsec.org.

• Black Arch: You can download BlackArch Linux
from https://blackarch.org and access the
documentation at
https://blackarch.org/guide.html. BlackArch Linux
source code can be accessed at
https://github.com/BlackArch/blackarch.
